222	 * discriminated `variant` (if any). The honeypot is rendered alongside (every
223	 * form carries one). The submit `<Button>` and the enclosing `<Form>` /
224	 * `FormProvider` stay the route's concern — `<FormFields />` is the field graph,
225	 * not the whole form shell.
226	 */
